# TDD Workflow Demo
# Records: /tdd slash command showing test-first development

Output images/tdd-workflow.gif
Set FontSize 14
Set Width 1400
Set Height 900
Set Theme "Dracula"
Set Padding 20
Set TypingSpeed 80ms
Set Shell "zsh"

Type "claude"
Enter
Sleep 5s

Type "/tdd Add an isPrime function"
Enter
Sleep 20s

# Accept permission prompt (Enter = Yes)
Enter
Sleep 10s

# Accept again if another prompt appears
Enter
Sleep 10s

Enter
Sleep 20s
